Package libshapedraw.primitive

Interface Summary
ReadonlyColor Read-only interface for Color objects, allowing for compile-time safety.
ReadonlyLineStyle Read-only interface for LineStyle objects, allowing for compile-time safety.
ReadonlyVector3 Read-only interface for Vector3 objects, allowing for compile-time safety.
 

Class Summary
Color Yet another class representing a Red/Green/Blue/Alpha color 4-tuple.
LineStyle Represent a line style: a Color and a floating point width.
Vector3 Yet another class representing a (X, Y, Z) vector or coordinate 3-tuple.
 

Enum Summary
Axis X/Y/Z axis, used by Vector3 convenience methods.
